{"tid":1472220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言。。。","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:49:26.000Z","uid":262794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eee765ecbee19f6a4613bfa723972b1b754d66b2","tid":1472220,"uid":262794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"淨係記得呢句?<br />\n<br />\n香港警察誓詞原文: <br />\n<br />\n本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切合法命令。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOHfZ6z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOHfZ6z.png&h=e38f29f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5cb665da8a3ef816bdd6ae92d6616f22f54e716","tid":1472220,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"班警犬唔識字㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識字就唔係狗啦"},{"pid":"042a537d067047868933eb045b84a13b1ca0e66f","tid":1472220,"uid":262794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5cb665da8a3ef816bdd6ae92d6616f22f54e716","tid":1472220,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"班警犬唔識字㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識字就唔係狗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:49:26.000Z","msg":"我想按讚的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}